Where the USE statement can be one of 4 following formats:
 1.FILE EXCEPTIONS procedures,
 2.DEBUGGING procedures,
 3.REPORTING procedures to be executed before the printing of the designated
   Report Group,
 4.EXCEPTION CONDITIONS procedures to be executed after detection of exception
   conditions.

